    "description": "<p>Beartic mace is an oleoresin capsicum tear gas aerosol that irritates the eyes with burning and pain sensations so intense so as to cause them to involuntarily close, bringing temporary blindness, with the pain otherwise affecting other motor capacities. Historically, mace has been a reliable and effective non-lethal self-defense tool.</p>",
